      <title>尼日利亚提高短期票据利率以吸引美元流入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/nigeria-hikes-rate-on-short-term-bills-to-lure-dollar-inflows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚央行为吸引投资者而提高短期债务利率后，一年期国债拍卖获得超额认购，这表明货币政策即将收紧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/nigeria-hikes-rate-on-short-term-bills-to-lure-dollar-inflows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 18:40:18 GMT</pubDate>
